---
---
<section class="impact-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="impact-header">
      <h2 class="impact-headline">Was sich in 8–12 Wochen ändert.</h2>
      <p class="impact-subline">Schluss mit Excel-Listen, Freitagnachmittag-Reports und Blindflug.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="impact-cards">
      <div class="impact-card impact-card--purple">
        <div class="impact-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="impact-title">Saubere Prozesse</h3>
        <p class="impact-text">Auditfähig bevor es jemand verlangt</p>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-card impact-card--cyan">
        <div class="impact-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M18 17V9"/><path d="M13 17V5"/><path d="M8 17v-3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="impact-title">Belastbare Daten</h3>
        <p class="impact-text">Echtzeit-Dashboards statt Excel-Listen</p>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-card impact-card--orange">
        <div class="impact-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="impact-title">24/7 Verfügbarkeit</h3>
        <p class="impact-text">Ihre Daten sind immer aktuell und abrufbar</p>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-card impact-card--amber">
        <div class="impact-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="impact-title">Lieferantenstatus sichern</h3>
        <p class="impact-text">Audit-ready bevor der OEM die Taskforce schickt</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .impact-strip {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .impact-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .impact-headline {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .impact-subline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .impact-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .impact-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .impact-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(50px);
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .impact-card--cyan::before {
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #0ea5e9 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .impact-card--purple::before {
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #a855f7 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .impact-card--orange::before {
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #f97316 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .impact-card--amber::before {
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #f59e0b 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .impact-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .impact-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .impact-icon {
    position: relative;
    color: #0ea5e9;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .impact-title {
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .impact-text {
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .impact-cards { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .impact-strip { padding: 3rem 0; }
    .impact-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .impact-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
